    <item>
      <title>菲律宾称中国在海上紧张局势中重新使用水炮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/philippines-says-ship-hit-by-water-cannon-from-china-vessel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾表示，三艘中国海警船在南海向两艘菲律宾船只发射了高压水枪，这是两国在争议海域紧张局势的最新升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/philippines-says-ship-hit-by-water-cannon-from-china-vessel</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 03:50:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>从哥伦比亚大学到加州大学洛杉矶分校，多所大学尝试停课，并通过对话平息校园抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/columbia-to-ucla-try-suspensions-talks-to-quell-campus-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着学年即将结束，从哥伦比亚大学到加州大学洛杉矶分校，美国各所大学都在急于应对亲巴勒斯坦示威活动，纪律处分不断升级，校园生活陷入混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/columbia-to-ucla-try-suspensions-talks-to-quell-campus-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 00:30:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>上议院称北爱尔兰面临失去兽药的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/northern-ireland-risks-losing-veterinary-medicines-lords-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[立法者警告说，由于英国脱欧规定，北爱尔兰将失去三分之一的兽药，这对公共健康构成威胁，并有可能导致英国食品供应链中断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/northern-ireland-risks-losing-veterinary-medicines-lords-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国在摩尔多瓦投票前对俄罗斯“混合”袭击发出警报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/uk-sounds-alarm-on-russian-hybrid-attacks-before-moldova-votes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉英国情报评估的人士透露，俄罗斯计划在摩尔多瓦总统选举和今年晚些时候举行的加入欧盟公投之前对摩尔多瓦发动一波所谓的“混合”攻击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/uk-sounds-alarm-on-russian-hybrid-attacks-before-moldova-votes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>警察死亡事件震惊智利，智利寻求更严格的安全法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/chile-seeks-tighter-security-laws-as-police-deaths-shock-country</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利政府正在呼吁更新安全措施和制定新的反恐法，因为该国正在努力解决周末三名警察被谋杀的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/chile-seeks-tighter-security-laws-as-police-deaths-shock-country</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 21:16:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>学术界警告称，中国持有的美国国债将成为“人质”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/china-s-us-assets-becoming-hostages-divestment-advocate-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家智库发表的一篇论文指出，中国需要进一步减持美国国债，部分原因是为了削弱华盛顿对其亚洲竞争对手的潜在影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/china-s-us-assets-becoming-hostages-divestment-advocate-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 21:08:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北卡罗来纳州家中发生枪战，四人死亡、四人受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-29/urgent-numerous-law-enforcement-officers-struck-by-gunfire-in-a-major-north-carolina-city-police-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北卡罗来纳州夏洛特（美联社）——警方称，周一在北卡罗来纳州一处住宅发生的枪战中，四名为一名因持有枪支而被通缉的重罪犯执行逮捕令的警官被杀，另外四名警官受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-29/urgent-numerous-law-enforcement-officers-struck-by-gunfire-in-a-major-north-carolina-city-police-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 18:40:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平的使命是挑拨欧洲和美国之间的关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/china-president-xi-to-visit-france-serbia-hungary-in-eu-charm-offensive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平五年来首次访问欧盟，并传达了一个明确的信息：北京为欧盟提供的经济机会比美国愿意承认的要多得多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/china-president-xi-to-visit-france-serbia-hungary-in-eu-charm-offensive</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 18:31:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚开始暂停不离开的学生抗议者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/columbia-says-it-was-unable-to-come-to-a-deal-with-protesters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚大学表示，已开始对那些违反下午 2 点截止时间离开西草坪的学生实施停课措施，此举进一步加剧了一周多前因巴勒斯坦人在这里扎营而引发的紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/columbia-says-it-was-unable-to-come-to-a-deal-with-protesters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 13:05:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
